## About This Dataset

### Description
This dataset was developed and structured by **Smartly AI** to support research and applications in the field of transliteration and semantic analysis. It is designed to be used in collaborative, academic, or professional projects.

### Purpose
- Provide an open and accessible dataset to enable research and technological development.  
- Encourage responsible and transparent use of data.

